txt.en: '[placeholder], there you are. I see my warrior found you. Your willingness to return is appreciated.'
Ningêna has sent a Dumûri to find you and relay her request for you to come talk to her at the Wrackwade.
You should travel to the Wrackwade and talk to Ningêna.

'Hashtal-gûr, [placeholder]. My captain, Ningêna, sent me to seek you out. She would like you to consider helping a man from Khûd Zagin to the south. He is insistent, and I feel she finds him rather irksome. She requests that you come to speak with her at the Wrackwade.'
